<subSubSection pageId="5" pageNumber="262" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="5.[810,1456,216,593]" box="[813,913,216,242]" pageId="5" pageNumber="262">REMARKS</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="5.[810,1456,216,593]" pageId="5" pageNumber="262">
The name 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Norman" authorityYear="1869" box="[918,1011,247,273]" class="Asteroidea" family="Ophidiasteridae" genus="Cribrella" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Valvatida" pageId="5" pageNumber="262" phylum="Echinodermata" rank="species" species="abyssicola">
<emphasis box="[918,1011,247,273]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="262">abyssicola</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
proposed by 
<bibRefCitation author="Perrier" box="[1143,1324,247,274]" firstAuthor="Perrier" journalOrPublisher="Annales des Sciences naturelles" page="24" pageId="5" pageNumber="262" pagination="1 - 72" part="6" refId="ref46489" refString="PERRIER E. 1885. - Premiere note preliminaire sur les echinodermes recueillis durant les campagnes de dragages sous-marins du Travailleur et du Talisman. Annales des Sciences naturelles (6) 19 (8): 1 - 72." title="Premiere note preliminaire sur les echinodermes recueillis durant les campagnes de dragages sous-marins du Travailleur et du Talisman" type="journal article" year="1885">Perrier (1885: 24)</bibRefCitation>
was changed in 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Perrier" authorityYear="1894" box="[842,927,279,305]" class="Asteroidea" family="Ophidiasteridae" genus="Cribrella" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Valvatida" pageId="5" pageNumber="262" phylum="Echinodermata" rank="species" species="abyssalis">
<emphasis box="[842,927,279,305]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="262">abyssalis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
by him in 1894 without explanation. The name 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Perrier" authorityYear="1894" box="[813,898,311,337]" class="Asteroidea" family="Ophidiasteridae" genus="Cribrella" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Valvatida" pageId="5" pageNumber="262" phylum="Echinodermata" rank="species" species="abyssalis">
<emphasis box="[813,898,311,337]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="262">abyssalis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
was then adopted by subsequent authors. It should be noted that Perrier still uses the name 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Norman" authorityYear="1869" box="[1261,1360,343,369]" class="Asteroidea" family="Ophidiasteridae" genus="Cribrella" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Valvatida" pageId="5" pageNumber="262" phylum="Echinodermata" rank="species" species="abyssicola">
<emphasis box="[1261,1360,343,369]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="262">abyssicola</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
in some tables in his 1894 work (see p. 30, 33 and 34).
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="5.[810,1456,216,593]" pageId="5" pageNumber="262">
Some of the 
<taxonomicName authorityName="de Folin" authorityYear="1887" box="[972,1067,406,432]" class="Gastropoda" family="Bursidae" genus="Talisman" kingdom="Animalia" order="Littorinimorpha" pageId="5" pageNumber="262" phylum="Mollusca" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[972,1067,406,432]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="262">Talisman</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
stations reported on museum labels differ from those in 
<bibRefCitation author="Perrier's" box="[1017,1176,438,465]" firstAuthor="Perrier's" pageId="5" pageNumber="262" pagination="1 - 431" refId="ref46625" refString="PERRIER E. 1894. - Stellerides. Resultats des Expeditions scientifiques du Travailleur et du Talisman. G. Masson, Paris 3: 1 - 431." type="journal article" year="1894">Perrier’s (1894)</bibRefCitation>
publication. This concerns either the locality or the number of individuals.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="5.[810,1456,216,593]" pageId="5" pageNumber="262">
To avoid confusion, note that 
<taxonomicName authority="Norman, 1869" authorityName="Norman" authorityYear="1869" class="Asteroidea" family="Ophidiasteridae" genus="Cribrella" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Valvatida" pageId="5" pageNumber="262" phylum="Echinodermata" rank="species" species="abyssicola">
<emphasis box="[1154,1351,502,528]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="262">Cribrella abyssicola</emphasis>
Norman, 1869
</taxonomicName>
is synonym of 
<taxonomicName authority="(O. F. Muller, 1776)" baseAuthorityName="O. F. Muller" baseAuthorityYear="1776" box="[1041,1454,534,561]" class="Asteroidea" family="Echinasteridae" genus="Henricia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Spinulosida" pageId="5" pageNumber="262" phylum="Echinodermata" rank="species" species="pertusa">
<emphasis box="[1041,1216,535,560]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="262">Henricia pertusa</emphasis>
(O. F. Müller, 1776)
</taxonomicName>
according to 
<bibRefCitation author="Madsen" box="[955,1124,566,593]" firstAuthor="Madsen" pageId="5" pageNumber="262" pagination="201 - 268" refId="ref45413" refString="MADSEN F. J. 1987. - The Henricia sanguinolenta complex (Echinodermata: Asteroidea) of the Norwegian Sea and adjacent waters. Steenstrupia 13: 201 - 268." type="journal article" year="1987">Madsen (1987)</bibRefCitation>
.
</paragraph>
